rows.label: qev085303_MSG0001
rows.name: Leland Cole, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0002
rows.name: That's right, missy! Who are you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0003
rows.name: Um, we're here to save you? Kiefer called in an SOS.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0004
rows.name: He did WHAT? ...Wait, did he already head back?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0005
rows.name: Yeah, and left you behind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0006
rows.name: Damn. He must have beat me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0007
rows.name: Hey, this isn't some race! He left you to die![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0008
rows.name:
Cole Family Rule Number Four:
When the job's done, go home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0009
rows.name:
Are all you people insane?
What the hell kind of family rule is that?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0010
rows.name: You folks are armed, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0011
rows.name: What? Well yeah, of course, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0012
rows.name: Good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0013
rows.name:
I still haven't grabbed all the ore in this cave
on account of the indigens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0014
rows.name: Could I get you kids to take care of that for me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0015
rows.name: Are you even listening to us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0016
rows.name:
Cole Family Rule Number Two:
Always finish the job, no matter what.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0017
rows.name:
'Sides, none of this stops New LA from needing
a secure source of flemtide, now does it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0018
rows.name: You are both insane, aren't you? All I'm saying isâ€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0019
rows.name: Fine. We'll do it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0020
rows.name: Colonel?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0021
rows.name:
They have their mission, we have ours.
If we can offer support, we will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0022
rows.name: Yes, ma'am...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0023
rows.name:
Flemtide is a bright red ore. Easy to spot.
Should be all over the cave.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085303_MSG0024
rows.name:
If you're so eager to help, try taking a look around for
the stuff.[ST:wait ]
